		<releaseNotes>This version of the Warehouse Management mobile app introduces the following fixes and improvements:
•Fixed an issue that caused pages to render incorrectly when users navigated from the Item Inquiry page to Custom pages.
•Fixed an issue where the Back button did not clear previously selected data when navigating between Item Inquiry pages.
•Fixed an issue where the ConnectionSetting parameter was not taken in consideration in MDM environments
•Fixed an issue where browser shortcuts appeared when users scanned a value.
•Improved he diagnostic file collection flow. Users can now save share or save in a local folder, useful for kiosk mode situations.
•Fixed an issue where, on the Movement flow’s Confirm page, users could not scan the license plate, only the last character of the barcode was shown.
•Fixed a visual issue where Work List tile headers were not parsed correctly when containing special characters.
•Fixed an issue in the Movement flow where the previous value was shown in the step banner on the wrong step.</releaseNotes>
